   <!--           We maintain 6 different app-descriptor files for this project - two                   -->
   <!--           each for Android, iOS and desktop versions. The desktop version is,                   -->
   <!--           more specifically, a 'desktop emulator' or 'desktop simulator' version                -->
   <!--           which we use when testing this (mobile only) app on the desktop.                      -->
   <!--           There are two copies of each of the three types because some of the info              -->
   <!--           in these files is private, and we maintain a private version, which we                -->
   <!--           use when compiling the project, and a public version which is included                -->
   <!--           in the publicly released version of our code. If you're using this public             -->
   <!--           code you should search these files for '##########' and provide                       -->
   <!--           replacements for this string. Also be aware that while we try to keep the             -->
   <!--           public version in sync with the private (aka 'actual') versions, you may              -->
   <!--           need to tweak the public versions a bit before you use them.                          -->
